Interface Callback<M>


  • public interface Callback<M>
    Callback is an interface that allows AsyncTasks to call functions from the main thread after the async task is finished.
    Author:
    itstc

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onComplete(M res)
